<!doctype html>
<html lang="es-ES">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Variant B — Architect's Cabinet · MIT Interiorismo</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@200;300;400;500&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0d0e0e;
    --bg-2: #131515;
    --bg-3: #1a1d1d;
    --line: #2a2e2e;
    --ink: #e8e6e1;
    --ink-soft: #b6b4af;
    --ink-muted: #6c6a66;
    --accent: #115a6b;
    --accent-2: #4c8390;
    --warm: #d4a373;
  }
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--ink); }
  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    letter-spacing: 0.005em;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }
  a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
  img { display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; }
  .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
  .num { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-muted); }

  /* LAYOUT — grid lines like an architect's cabinet */
  .frame { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr 1fr 1fr; min-height: 100vh; }
  .frame-line { border-left: 1px solid var(--line); }
  aside { padding: 28px 22px; border-right: 1px solid var(--line); }

  /* NAV vertical */
  nav.vertical {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 24px 0; height: 100vh; position: sticky; top: 0;
  }
  nav.vertical .vert-logo { writing-mode: vertical-rl; transform: rotate(180deg); font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 20px 0; }
  nav.vertical .vert-logo em { font-style: normal; color: var(--accent-2); }
  nav.vertical .vert-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 20px 0; }
  nav.vertical .vert-links a { padding: 6px 0; }
  nav.vertical .vert-meta { font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-muted); writing-mode: vertical-rl; padding: 20px 0; }

  .tag-variant {
    position: fixed; bottom: 24px; right: 32px; z-index: 60;
    background: var(--accent); color: var(--ink); padding: 6px 14px;
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* HERO — asimetric, monochrome */
  .hero {
    grid-column: 2 / -1;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 7fr 5fr;
    min-height: 100vh;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .hero-img { position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero-img img { position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; filter: grayscale(0.3) contrast(1.05) brightness(0.85); }
  .hero-img::before {
    content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 70%, var(--bg) 100%);
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .hero-img-caption {
    position: absolute; bottom: 24px; left: 24px; z-index: 3;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(232,230,225,0.6); letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  .hero-body { padding: 64px 56px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; background: var(--bg); }
  .hero-eyebrow { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: var(--accent-2); letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .hero-title { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 200; font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5.5rem); line-height: 1.02; letter-spacing: -0.025em; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .hero-title .mark { color: var(--accent-2); font-weight: 300; }
  .hero-meta { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 32px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); padding-top: 28px; }
  .hero-meta dt { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-muted); letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .hero-meta dd { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.4; }
  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
    padding: 14px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--ink); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  /* SECTION LABEL */
  .section-bar {
    grid-column: 2 / -1;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 7fr 5fr;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .section-label {
    padding: 20px 56px; border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-muted);
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  }
  .section-label .index { color: var(--accent-2); }

  /* MANIFIESTO */
  .manifesto {
    grid-column: 2 / -1; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 7fr 5fr;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .manifesto-body { padding: 96px 56px; border-right: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .manifesto-body h2 { font-weight: 200; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.015em; max-width: 22ch; }
  .manifesto-body h2 .mark { color: var(--accent-2); }
  .manifesto-body p { margin-top: 32px; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 50ch; }
  .manifesto-side { padding: 96px 56px; background: var(--bg-2); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 28px; justify-content: center; }
  .manifesto-quote { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 200; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.35; letter-spacing: -0.015em; }
  .manifesto-quote .mark { color: var(--accent-2); }
  .manifesto-attribution { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-muted); letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; }

  /* PROYECTOS — table/cabinet style */
  .projects { grid-column: 2 / -1; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .projects-header { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 4fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; padding: 24px 56px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-muted); }
  .project-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 4fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px; padding: 0 56px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    transition: background 0.4s;
  }
  .project-row:hover { background: var(--bg-2); }
  .project-row .cell { padding: 32px 0; border-right: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .project-row .cell:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .project-row .ph { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 200; font-size: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; padding-right: 24px; }
  .project-row .num { font-size: 13px; color: var(--accent-2); }
  .project-row .meta-line { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-muted); }
  .project-row .meta-line strong { color: var(--ink); display: block; }
  .project-row .status { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: var(--warm); letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .project-row .cta { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 14px 16px; border: 1px solid var(--line); align-self: center; width: fit-content; }

  /* PHILOSOPHY grid */
  .philosophy { grid-column: 2 / -1; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .phi-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 0; }
  .phi-cell { padding: 64px 32px; border-right: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .phi-cell:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .phi-num { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: var(--accent-2); letter-spacing: 0.2em; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .phi-cell h3 { font-weight: 200; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.015em; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .phi-cell p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--ink-soft); }

  /* CTA */
  .cta { grid-column: 2 / -1; padding: 96px 56px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 7fr 5fr; gap: 60px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .cta h2 { font-weight: 200; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem); line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.025em; }
  .cta h2 .mark { color: var(--accent-2); }
  .cta-side { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; justify-content: center; }
  .cta-side p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--ink-soft); }
  .cta-side a { padding: 18px 24px; background: var(--ink); color: var(--bg); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; width: fit-content; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer { grid-column: 2 / -1; padding: 32px 56px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 32px; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  footer h5 { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: var(--ink-muted); letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  footer p, footer a { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink-soft); }

  /* responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1100px) { .frame { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } aside, nav.vertical { display: none; } .hero, .manifesto, .cta { grid-column: 1; grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .hero-img { min-height: 60vh; } .section-bar { grid-column: 1; grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .projects { grid-column: 1; } .projects-header { display: none; } .project-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 32px 24px; gap: 0; } .project-row .cell { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 12px 0; } .philosophy { grid-column: 1; } .phi-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .phi-cell { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); } footer { grid-column: 1; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; padding: 32px 24px; } }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .hero-body, .manifesto-body, .manifesto-side, .cta, footer { padding-left: 24px; padding-right: 24px; } }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="tag-variant">Concepto B · Architect's Cabinet</div>

<div class="frame">
  <aside>
    <nav class="vertical">
      <div class="vert-logo">mit <em>·</em> interiorismo</div>
      <div class="vert-links">
        <a href="#">Index</a>
        <a href="#">Projects</a>
        <a href="#">Studio</a>
        <a href="#">Process</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
      </div>
      <div class="vert-meta">YÉCORA · ES</div>
    </nav>
  </aside>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-img">
      <img src="/images/hero/hero-oficina-luciano.jpg" alt="Oficina en proyecto Luciano" />
      <div class="hero-img-caption">PL.001 — Oficina principal — Logroño</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-body">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">F.01 · Hero — Estudio · 2026</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Donde el <span class="mark">diseño</span> encuentra a la <span class="mark">ingeniería</span>.</h1>
      <dl class="hero-meta">
        <div><dt>Estudio</dt><dd>mit interiorismo</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Localización</dt><dd>Yécora · Álava</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Activo desde</dt><dd>2020</dd></div>
      </dl>
      <a href="#" class="hero-cta">→  Ver proyectos — 4 casos</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-bar">
    <div class="section-label"><span>F.02 · Manifiesto</span><span class="index">02 / 06</span></div>
    <div class="section-label"></div>
  </div>

  <section class="manifesto">
    <div class="manifesto-body">
      <h2>Un estudio boutique que une lo que normalmente va separado: <span class="mark">el diseño y la ingeniería</span>.</h2>
      <p>Diseño + instalaciones + normativa, todo bajo un mismo proyecto. Defensa técnica del cliente frente a gremios, proveedores y sorpresas de obra.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="manifesto-side">
      <p class="manifesto-quote">"Soy la aliada técnica del cliente. Si un instalador cobra de más, lo advierto."</p>
      <p class="manifesto-attribution">— María Iturbe Sánchez · Fundadora</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-bar">
    <div class="section-label"><span>F.03 · Trabajos 2026 · Selección</span><span class="index">03 / 06</span></div>
    <div class="section-label"></div>
  </div>

  <section class="projects">
    <div class="projects-header">
      <div>Caso</div><div>Localización / Tipo</div><div>Sup.</div><div>Año</div><div>Estado</div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-row">
      <div class="cell ph">Proyecto Luciano</div>
      <div class="cell"><p class="meta-line"><strong>Logroño · La Rioja</strong></p><p class="meta-line">Cambio de uso oficinas → 2 viviendas + oficina</p></div>
      <div class="cell num">133 m²</div>
      <div class="cell num">'26</div>
      <div class="cell"><span class="status">Anteproyecto</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-row">
      <div class="cell ph">EFITAR Ingeniería</div>
      <div class="cell"><p class="meta-line"><strong>Logroño · La Rioja</strong></p><p class="meta-line">Reforma comercial → oficina técnica</p></div>
      <div class="cell num">107 m²</div>
      <div class="cell num">'26</div>
      <div class="cell"><span class="status">Presupuesto</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-row">
      <div class="cell ph">Berceo 36</div>
      <div class="cell"><p class="meta-line"><strong>Logroño · La Rioja</strong></p><p class="meta-line">Reforma integral + aerotermia</p></div>
      <div class="cell num">80 m²</div>
      <div class="cell num">'26</div>
      <div class="cell"><span class="status">En curso</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="project-row">
      <div class="cell ph">Haro · climatización</div>
      <div class="cell"><p class="meta-line"><strong>Haro · La Rioja</strong></p><p class="meta-line">Asesoría técnica · ahorro 68%</p></div>
      <div class="cell num">40 m²</div>
      <div class="cell num">'26</div>
      <div class="cell"><span class="status">Completado</span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-bar">
    <div class="section-label"><span>F.04 · Principios</span><span class="index">04 / 06</span></div>
    <div class="section-label"></div>
  </div>

  <section class="philosophy">
    <div class="phi-grid">
      <div class="phi-cell">
        <div class="phi-num">001</div>
        <h3>Diseño + técnica, juntos</h3>
        <p>La mayoría de interioristas trabajan solo con la estética. MIT proyecta también las instalaciones: eléctricas, climatización, fontanería.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="phi-cell">
        <div class="phi-num">002</div>
        <h3>Presupuestos transparentes</h3>
        <p>Cada partida, cada medición, cada proveedor. Si un instalador cobra de más, lo advierto.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="phi-cell">
        <div class="phi-num">003</div>
        <h3>Defensa técnica del cliente</h3>
        <p>Aliada frente a gremios, proveedores y sorpresas de obra. Traducción de normativa CTE / REBT / RITE.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="phi-cell">
        <div class="phi-num">004</div>
        <h3>Boutique, no franquicia</h3>
        <p>Un solo interlocutor, de principio a fin. Honorarios fijos en torno al 11% s/PEM.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-bar">
    <div class="section-label"><span>F.05 · Contacto</span><span class="index">05 / 06</span></div>
    <div class="section-label"></div>
  </div>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>¿Tienes un <span class="mark">proyecto</span> en mente?</h2>
    <div class="cta-side">
      <p>La primera consulta es siempre sin compromiso. Te respondemos en menos de 48h con una primera valoración y los siguientes pasos.</p>
      <a href="mailto:hola@mitinteriorismo.studio">Empezar un proyecto →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div><h5>Estudio</h5><p>mit interiorismo<br/>María Iturbe Sánchez<br/>Yécora, Álava</p></div>
    <div><h5>Contacto</h5><p><a href="mailto:hola@mitinteriorismo.studio">hola@mitinteriorismo.studio</a></p></div>
    <div><h5>Zona</h5><p>La Rioja<br/>Álava · País Vasco</p></div>
    <div><h5>Concepto</h5><p style="color:var(--accent-2)">B · Architect's Cabinet</p></div>
  </footer>
</div>

</body>
</html>
